    "intro": [
      "I'm a creative entrepreneur guided by my God-given talent to reveal the natural beauty of the world — both in people and the planet.",
      "Through my work, I strive to inspire and empower others by showcasing the authentic and extraordinary moments that surround us, helping people see and celebrate their unique light while honoring the beauty of nature.",
      "Friends and clients call me Cait."
    ],
    "story": [
      "I've always been gifted with a natural creative ability — one that lets me see the world in a way that's uniquely mine.",
      "Through my lens and stories, I capture the beauty and truth that often go unnoticed, both in people and the world around us. Inspired by my travels and life's twists — including a corporate layoff that became a turning point — I chose to lean into this gift and share my vision with others.",
      "For me, creativity is more than just art. It's a way to honor the light within each moment and every soul I encounter. Now, as a content creator and photographer, I'm committed to showing the world through my eyes — inviting others to find their own beauty and purpose along the way."
    ],
